javaxipc30
Class QidList

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--javaxipc30.QidList
public final class QidList
extends java.lang.Object

A QidList represents a list of QueSys message queue id's. For message retrieval operations, the queue id's may have message select codes applied. The methods of this class are alternatives, with a more object oriented flavor, to the Xipc.MemListBuild() and Xipc.MemListAdd() methods.

See Also:
Xipc.QueListBuild(int), Xipc.QueListAdd(javaxipc30.QidList, int)
